WEBVTT

02:51.254 --> 02:55.425
My dear, I love you so much.
I can't handle this. How wonderful!

02:55.508 --> 02:56.759
Oh, stop, Mom.

02:59.971 --> 03:01.306
Uh, yeah. He can.

03:12.775 --> 03:16.446
Oh, how can you
stay mad at him? You just can't!

03:46.476 --> 03:49.479
Oh, Miguel,
are you going to visit your girlfriend?

03:49.562 --> 03:51.189
I bet she misses you.
